description: Ketosis is a normal metabolic process, something your body does to keep working. When it doesn't have enough carbohydrates from food for your cells to burn for energy, it burns fat instead. This skill provides facts about Ketosis and Ketogenic(Keto) Diets.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask keto facts to tell me something
Alexa, ask keto facts to tell me a fact about the ketogenic diet
Alexa, ask keto facts to give me some information about ketogenic diets
name: KetoFacts
shortDescription: Ketosis is a state of body function where your body burns fat for energy when carbohydrates are in short supply. Learn more by asking for a "Keto Fact".
